            <td>Budget. Purpose-built for China. Works on mobile + desktop.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong><a href="https://protonvpn.com" rel="nofollow">ProtonVPN</a></strong></td>
            <td>✅ Yes (Stealth protocol)</td>
            <td>Free tier / $9.99/mo</td>
            <td>Privacy-focused. Free tier works but is slow. Paid tier with Stealth protocol works well.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>AstrillVPN</strong></td>
            <td>✅ Yes</td>
            <td>$15–30/mo</td>
            <td>Most reliable historically, but expensive. Popular among expats.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>LetsVPN</strong></td>
